<view class="page"><view class="topbar">校园奖项<text class="en">ACHIEVEMENTS</text></view><view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="neo-card">正在计算奖项进度…</view><view wx:for="{{achievements}}" wx:key="id" class="award-card {{item.unlocked ? 'unlocked' : 'locked'}}"><view class="award-icon"><image src="{{item.iconPath}}" mode="aspectFit" /></view><view class="award-copy"><view class="award-name">{{item.name}}</view><view class="award-desc">{{item.description}}</view><view class="progress"><view style="width: {{item.progress / item.target * 100}}%" /></view><view class="number">{{item.progress}} / {{item.target}}</view></view></view><view class="note">风险复核中的交接不会提前计入奖项；管理员撤销无效交接后，进度会从有效记录重新计算。</view></view>
